<div class="bg-[#151926] rounded-xl border border-gray-800 p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-2xl">
<h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8 border-b border-gray-800 pb-6">
                    Quravel Comprehensive Guide, Rules &amp; Regulations
                </h1>
<section class="mb-10">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Welcome to Quravel</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Your premier destination for streaming movies and shows. This guide ensures a safe, enjoyable experience for all users.
                    </p>
</section>
<hr class="border-gray-800 my-8"/>
<section class="mb-10">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">I. Account &amp; Usage Guidelines</h2>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Account Creation &amp; Security</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>Users must be at least 13 years old (or the minimum age in their country) to create an account.</li>
<li>Provide accurate, current information during registration.</li>
<li>One account per user; sharing credentials is prohibited.</li>
<li>You are responsible for all activity under your account.</li>
<li>Notify Quravel immediately of any unauthorized access.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Subscription &amp; Billing</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>Choose from Free (ad-supported) or Premium (ad-free) plans.</li>
<li>Billing cycles are monthly or annually, auto-renewing unless canceled.</li>
<li>Cancel anytime; no refunds for partial periods except where required by law.</li>
<li>Prices and plans are subject to change with prior notice.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<hr class="border-gray-800 my-8"/>
<section class="mb-10">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">II. Content &amp; Streaming Rules</h2>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Authorized Use</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>Streaming is for personal, non-commercial use only.</li>
<li>Download features (if available) are for offline viewing on personal devices.</li>
<li>Do not redistribute, broadcast, or publicly screen content without permission.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Prohibited Actions</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>No reverse-engineering, copying, or scraping Quravel’s content or technology.</li>
<li>No use of VPNs or proxies to circumvent regional licensing restrictions.</li>
<li>No attempt to bypass security, ads, or digital rights management (DRM).</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<hr class="border-gray-800 my-8"/>
<section class="mb-10">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">III. User Conduct &amp; Community</h2>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Respectful Interaction</h3>
<p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">Reviews, comments, and profiles must not contain:</p>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300 mb-4">
<li>Hate speech, harassment, or threats.</li>
<li>Spam, advertisements, or off-topic content.</li>
<li>Spoilers without warning.</li>
<li>Personally identifiable information of others.</li>
</ul>
<p class="text-gray-300">Quravel may remove inappropriate content or suspend accounts at its discretion.</p>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Legal Compliance</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>You agree to use Quravel in compliance with all local, national, and international laws.</li>
<li>You are responsible for ensuring your use of Quravel is legal in your jurisdiction.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<hr class="border-gray-800 my-8"/>
<section class="mb-10">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">IV. Intellectual Property</h2>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Copyright</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>All content on Quravel is owned by Quravel or its licensors.</li>
<li>Unauthorized recording, distribution, or modification of content is prohibited.</li>
<li>Report suspected copyright infringement via our designated contact.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Your Content</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>By submitting reviews or user-generated content, you grant Quravel a license to display it.</li>
<li>You affirm you have the rights to any content you submit.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<hr class="border-gray-800 my-8"/>
<section class="mb-10">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">V. Privacy &amp; Data</h2>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data Collection</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>We collect data as described in our <a class="text-primary hover:underline" href="#">Privacy Policy</a> (separate document).</li>
<li>Data may include viewing history, device information, and preferences.</li>
<li>We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data Usage</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>Data is used to personalize recommendations, improve service, and process payments.</li>
<li>We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</li>
<li>You may request account deletion, subject to legal retention requirements.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<hr class="border-gray-800 my-8"/>
<section class="mb-10">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">VI. Disclaimers &amp; Limitations</h2>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Service Availability</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>Quravel is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind.</li>
<li>We do not guarantee uninterrupted, error-free, or available service.</li>
<li>Content library varies by region and may change without notice.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Liability</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>Quravel is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.</li>
<li>Our total liability is limited to the amount you paid in the last 12 months.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<hr class="border-gray-800 my-8"/>
<section class="mb-10">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">VII. Termination &amp; Changes</h2>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Termination</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>Quravel may suspend or terminate accounts for violations of these rules.</li>
<li>You may terminate your account at any time.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Policy Updates</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>Quravel may update these rules periodically.</li>
<li>Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.</li>
<li>Significant changes will be notified via email or in-app notice.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<hr class="border-gray-800 my-8"/>
<section class="mb-12">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">VIII. Contact &amp; Support</h2>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">For Support</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>Visit <a class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline" href="#">help.quravel.com</a> for FAQs and troubleshooting.</li>
<li>Contact support at <a class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline" href="mailto:support@quravel.com">support@quravel.com</a> for account issues.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Legal Inquiries</h3>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-300">
<li>For copyright, legal notices, or law enforcement requests:</li>
<li class="list-none pt-2"><a class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline" href="mailto:legal@quravel.com">legal@quravel.com</a></li>
